         <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p><note>i</note>: In Christ. In this tomb lies the body of [ ?of good memory . . . he passed from this] world in the year
                six thousand, 400 [and ninety]eight, third indiction [ . . . ] day 4 in the month October. May he have rest eternal.</p>
            <p><note>ii</note>: I will hope [in you Lord] that I may not be confounded for eternity. 
               In your justice liberate me and rescue me, my God and my Lord and my Saviour. Pray for me that I may have God as my protector in the day of judgement. Amen, Amen, Amen.</p>
